  "title": "STRUCTURAL ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</strong></p><p>CSCE PTE. LTD.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will prepare structural designs and analyses aligned with Eurocode and Singapore Standards, develop detailed structural drawings, and manage documentation for regulatory submissions. You will collaborate with clients, contractors, and authorities to ensure project compliance and progress.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform structural design and analysis following Eurocode and Singapore Standards to ensure safety and compliance</li><li>Develop detailed structural drawings that accurately reflect design specifications and client requirements</li><li>Prepare and incorporate design queries from clients and contractors to resolve technical issues promptly</li><li>Compile structural plans, design reports, and other documentation for submission to relevant authorities</li><li>Produce HDB, PUB, and BCA drawings tailored to their specific submission requirements</li><li>Participate actively in project progress, technical, and contractor meetings to facilitate effective communication and project alignment</li><li>Prepare and document tendering works to support project bidding and procurement processes</li><li>Coordinate project activities across multidisciplinary teams to ensure timely delivery and quality outcomes</li></ul>",
